    "In many cases, these linear models outperform most Transformer-based models in the area of time series forecasting.",
    "Decomposition of time seriesEntangled temporal features in multivariate time series forecasting present significant challenges when it comes to effectively exploring local and long-range dependencies among time points and variables 41.",
    "Many methods identify temporal dependencies with entangled temporal patterns, but they often can hardly fully leverage the inherent complex features of time series data, such as seasonality and trends.",
    "Therefore, various studies adopt time series decomposition to analyze time series.",
    "These decomposition methods can be divided into three categories: frequency domain decomposition, time domain decomposition, and time-frequency domain decomposition."
